    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This driver-focused example features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving powerplant is mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent technical attention includes a comprehensive VANOS service and valve clearance adjustment. The chassis remains structurally sound with no signs of rear subframe fatigue, while the suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics. A mechanically honest car ready for the apex, offering the raw, analog feedback characteristic of this iconic platform.",
