      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, super reliable, and it still runs like a dream. It\u2019s perfect if you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for its next adventure. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
