    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a hallmark of analog performance. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. This example features critical preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and recent valve lash adjustments. The suspension maintains factory geometry with upgraded polyurethane bushings for enhanced lateral stiffness. While the aesthetic reflects its 'good' driver-quality status, the powertrain and chassis dynamics remain sharp and responsive. A purist\u2019s specification for those valuing mechanical provenance over concours perfection.",
